It was so much fun creating the first location of many for @thebougiegrazer 

My client is a visionary in her field, a food stylist and creator of the Champagne & Charcuterie Workshop and knows what she wants!

She’s been featured on Good Day Atlanta and makes the best epic and elevated graze tables and trays in Atlanta. 

I designed her space to be an event space, workshop, eatery and workspace. I wanted it to have picture moments at every angle with bold colors, and a floral-vintage maximalist concept.

The epoxy bar, velvet fuchsia upholstered seating, and under staircase shelving install, are all custom designed and built.

I couldn’t of brought this vision to life without my right hand @willliamsresurfacing she is the best and puts up with me 😂🙏🏾 and contractor Eddie.
 
Location 2 coming soon!
